6. MINTING SYSTEM (STRICT RULE SET)

Core Constraints

❌ No allowance

❌ No burn

❌ No selfdestruct

❌ No liquidity or DeFi logic

❌ No ETH stored in contract

❌ No self-mint

Permissionless Mint

> Minting is permissionless but requires gas cost

any address can mint to any other address

no approval required

gas cost acts as natural constraint

Atomic Mint Definition

> Atomic mint = one transaction mints the smallest possible unit (1 SOS)

1 transaction = 1 unit

no batching

no fractional mint

minimal emission per interaction

Mint as Interaction

> Mint is not issuance — it is a relational event between two addresses

always address → address

never self-mint

forms the base signal of the system



